bdi4jade.goal

Class BeliefNotNullValueGoal<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bdi4jade.goal.AbstractBeliefGoal<K>
      • bdi4jade.goal.BeliefNotNullValueGoal<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the belief name.
    V - the type of the belief value.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeliefGoal<K>, Goal, jade.content.Concept, jade.content.ContentElement, jade.content.Term, java.io.Serializable

    public class BeliefNotNullValueGoal<K,V>
extends AbstractBeliefGoal<K>
    This class represents the goal of an agent to believe in a certain belief with a not null value, that is, the agent has a belief whose name is specified in this goal and value can be any but null.
    Author:
    Ingrid Nunes
